OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy with further outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain likely, some heavy bursts over
OL,7,Fthe hills and moors. The rain breaking
OL,8,Finto showers, perhaps thundery during
OL,9,Fthe afternoon. Brighter spells
OL,10,Fpossible later.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FShowers easing during Monday and
OL,14,FTuesday with sunnier spells emerging.
OL,15,FSimilar on Wednesday with variable
OL,16,Famounts of cloud, feeling fresher than
OL,17,Frecent days as temperatures fall away.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
